    "description": "Residential refrigerator freezer-compartment diagnostic and repair across all five SoCal counties. Defrost system service (heater, thermostat, timer trifecta), door seal replacement (frost on back wall), evaporator fan motor (freezer-side specific), temperature sensor drift correction (too cold or too warm complaints), built-in column architecture (Sub-Zero 700-series), garage freezer ambient temperature issues. Sub-Zero, Wolf (residential cooktops and ranges, freezer drawer integration), KitchenAid built-in, LG French-door, Samsung French-door, Whirlpool side-by-side, Frigidaire (chest and upright garage freezer angle), Maytag, GE Profile / Café / Monogram (Haier-owned since 2016), Bosch, Thermador, Miele, Liebherr (German independent). $89 residential diagnostic, waived with repair. BHGS #A49573, EPA 608 Universal certified #1346255700410.",
